        "type": "email",
        "html": "<p>Hello {first_name, \"there\"},</p><p>It's allegedly mid-week, but who knows what day it is any more?</p><p>I don't know about you, but I'm having to actively isolate myself from Twitter, because what's developing in the US is almost compulsive viewing. It feels almost bizarre to be writing newsletters like this with the background of journalists being aggressively targeted by the police in a major western democracy. But, I need to keep reminding myself, one of the responses open to us is get better at doing what we do. Hopefully today's digest will help you with that.</p><p>Stay safe, my friends.</p>"
